CustomField.description: Determines the load order for the Accounting Sets if you have multiple sets. Lower numbers will run first. For example, load order 1 runs before load order 2.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If you have more than one Accounting Set, your load order determines the sequence at which they run. The lower number will run first. For example, load order 1 will run before load order 2.
CustomField.label: Load Order
